headline.print_headline: Well-Known Humpback Whale Killed in Boat Collision
headline.main: Well-Known Humpback Whale Killed in Boat Collision

lead_paragraph: Federal law enforcement officials are investigating after a 48-foot female whale well-known in the waters of southeast Alaska was killed in a collision with a boat.
